title: DC SHOES: 2013 NZ/AU TOUR
description:
The DC team takes over New Zealand and Australia in this 2013 NZ/AU Tour video. Featuring Chris Cole, Nyjah Huston, Wes Kremer, Mikey Taylor, Mike Mo Capaldi, Evan Smith, Davis Torgerson, Madars Apse and Cyril Jackson. Also featuring DC APAC's Tommy Fynn, Jake Hayes, Bugs Fardell, Joel Mcilroy and Deon Williams. 

Defined By DC
